topic.title: Yellow Vests: Act 5
topic.body:
Thousands of people are walking on in Paris to protest against the French president macron. French workers are fed up to pay for the immigrants and other people who don't want to work (and pay nothing ...). Other countries follow the movement, in Germany, Belgium and on..
We fight for freedom, justice and non-islamism.
If nothing is displayed on TV, it's censorship of course. 
Have a nice day and thank you all !
